Company Overview of Santander UK Group Holdings plc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Santander UK Group Holdings plc, together with its subsidiaries, provides a range of banking products and services in the United Kingdom and internationally. The company operates through Retailing Banking, Commercial Banking, and Global Corporate Banking segments. The Retail Banking segment provides residential mortgage loans, savings and current accounts, credit cards, personal loans, insurance policies, and vehicle finance products to individuals and small businesses through a network of branches and ATMs, as well as through telephony, digital, mobile, and intermediary channels. The Commercial Banking segment offers loans, bank accounts, and deposits; and treasury, invoice discounting, cas...
Santander UK Group Holdings plc, together with its subsidiaries, provides a range of banking products and services in the United Kingdom and internationally. The company operates through Retailing Banking, Commercial Banking, and Global Corporate Banking segments. The Retail Banking segment provides residential mortgage loans, savings and current accounts, credit cards, personal loans, insurance policies, and vehicle finance products to individuals and small businesses through a network of branches and ATMs, as well as through telephony, digital, mobile, and intermediary channels. The Commercial Banking segment offers loans, bank accounts, and deposits; and treasury, invoice discounting, cash transmission, trade finance, and asset finance services to small and medium enterprises, mid corporates, and commercial real estate and social housing customers through a network of regional business centers, and telephony and digital channels. The Global Corporate Banking segment holds securities issued by local and central governments, and government guaranteed counterparties; and provides loans and treasury products for large corporates to support their working capital and liquidity needs, as well as derivatives, repurchase and reverse repurchase transactions, and stock borrowing/lending services. The company was founded in 1944 and is based in London, the United Kingdom. Santander UK Group Holdings plc operates as a subsidiary of Banco Santander, S.A.
