Santander UK

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Santander UK plc





Type

Public limited company


Industry
Finance and Insurance


Founded
11 January 2010


Headquarters
London, England, UK



Key people

Baroness Vadera, Chairwoman
Nathan Bostock, CEO


Products
Financial Services


Revenue
£4.573 billion (2015)[1]



